03/31/83  char_bit_offset_fcns_

Six subroutines are available for the manipulation of the character
and bit offsets of pointers:

char_offset_
   returns the character offset of a pointer.
add_char_offset_
   adds a displacement to the character offset of a pointer.
set_char_offset_
   sets the character offset of a pointer.
bit_offset_
   returns the bit offset of a pointer.
add_bit_offset_
   adds a displacement to the bit offset of a pointer
set_bit_offset_
   sets the bit offset of a pointer.

To obtain information on an individual subroutine, type:
           help SUBROUTINE_NAME
